                    Ac dictum risus sagittis id morbi posu justo eleifend libero ultricies
                </p>
                <button class="btn btn-block">Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel-rel col-sm-4">
            <img class="media-object" src="~/images/my_trainings/overdue.png" alt="...">
            <div class="panel-body pad-top60">
                <h4 class="panel-title">Overdue Courses</h4>
                <p>
                    Fusce gravida tortor felis
                    Ac dictum risus sagittis id morbi posu justo eleifend libero ultricies
                </p>
                <button class="btn btn-block">Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel-rel col-sm-4">
            <img class="media-object" src="~/images/my_trainings/completed.png" alt="...">
            <div class="panel-body pad-top60">
                <h4 class="panel-title">Completed</h4>
                <p>
                    Fusce gravida tortor felis
                    Ac dictum risus sagittis id morbi posu justo eleifend libero ultricies
                </p>
                <button class="btn btn-block">Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="space40"></div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="panel-rel">
                <div class="panel-body">

                    <div class="profile-container col-sm-5">
                        <div class="grey-circle">
                            <img class="profile-img" src="~/images/profile.jpg" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h4 ng-cloak><strong>{{ user.firstName }}</strong> {{ user.lastName }}</h4>
                            <p>{{ user.primaryBusinessRole.name }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="badge-container col-sm-7">
                        <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4">
                            <img src="~/images/my_trainings/badge_yellow.png" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4">
                            <img src="~/images/my_trainings/badge_green.png" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4">
                            <img src="~/images/my_trainings/badge_violet.png" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4">
                            <img src="~/images/my_trainings/badge_pink.png" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4">
                            <img src="~/images/my_trainings/badge_red.png" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4">
                            <img src="~/images/my_trainings/badge_orange.png" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-footer">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="panel-rel">
                            <div class="rewards-container col-sm-2">
                                <p>Rewards</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-sm-5">
                                <label class="lbl-achievements">Your Latest Achievements</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-5 img-group">
                                <img class="achievement" src="~/images/my_trainings/achievement_1.png" />
                                <img class="achievement" src="~/images/my_trainings/achievement_2.png" />
                                <img class="achievement" src="~/images/my_trainings/achievement_3.png" />
                                <img class="achievement" src="~/images/my_trainings/achievement_4.png" />
                                <button class="btn btn-default pull-right">View All</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel-rel">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <div class="profile-container">
                        <div class="col-sm-8">
                            <h4>Certificates</h4>
                            <p>Your latest Certificates</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-4"><button class="btn btn-default">View All</button></div>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-footer">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-12 img-group">
                            <img class="achievement" src="~/images/my_trainings/certificate_1.png" />
                            <img class="achievement" src="~/images/my_trainings/certificate_2.png" />
                            <button class="btn btn-default pull-right">View All</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space40"></div>

    <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
        <li class="active"><a href="#training" data-toggle="tab">Trainings</a></li>
        <li><a href="#invitations" data-toggle="tab">Training Invitations</a></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="tab-content">
            <div id="training" class="tab-pane active">
                <div class="listing col-md-6">
                    <div class="listing-title">
                        <h4>First Aid Training  </h4>
                        <h4 class="sp-strong title-right">Petter Pharmacy</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="listing-container bg-white">
                        <div class="row listing-row">
                            <p>
                                Recommended for parents, grandparents or those caring for children and/or babies. Learn what to do if a child or baby starts choking,
                                becomes unresponsive or swallows something harmful. Includes training for medical emergencies such as meningitis and asthma.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="listing col-md-6">
                    <div class="listing-title">
                        <h4>First Aid Training  </h4>
                        <h4 class="sp-strong title-right">Petter Pharmacy</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="listing-container bg-white">
                        <div class="row listing-row">
                            <p>
                                Suitable for people who work in low hazard environments or where Health and Safety Executive (HSE) guidelines indicate staff should
                                hold a certificate in emergency first aid at work.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tab-pane" id="invitations">
                <ul>
                    <li></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>